A:/> C:
C:/> 
C:/> # ============================================================
C:/> 
C:/> # Fill Disk Torture Test
C:/> 
C:/> # Tests that the filesystem handles disk-full conditions
C:/> 
C:/> # correctly: proper error reporting, existing files remain
C:/> 
C:/> # accessible, and space is recoverable after deletion.
C:/> 
C:/> #
C:/> 
C:/> # Strategy:
C:/> 
C:/> #   1. Check initial free space
C:/> 
C:/> #   2. Create large files to consume nearly all blocks
C:/> 
C:/> #   3. Attempt to create a file on a full disk (expect error)
C:/> 
C:/> #   4. Verify existing files are still readable
C:/> 
C:/> #   5. Delete files and verify space is recovered
C:/> 
C:/> #   6. Create a file in recovered space to prove reuse works
C:/> 
C:/> #   7. Clean up
C:/> 
C:/> # ============================================================
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 1: Record initial free space
C:/> 
C:/> FREE
Free Blocks:  948736 bytes (1853 blocks)
Free Memory:  47087 bytes
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 2: Fill the disk with large files
C:/> 
C:/> # Each 60000-byte file uses 118 data blocks + 1 inode = 119 blocks
C:/> 
C:/> # 15 files = 1785 blocks, leaving ~90 free
C:/> 
C:/> RANDDATA FILL01.DAT 60000 1001
50127 118
C:/> 
C:/> RANDDATA FILL02.DAT 60000 2002
50275 118
C:/> 
C:/> RANDDATA FILL03.DAT 60000 3003
52059 118
C:/> 
C:/> RANDDATA FILL04.DAT 60000 4004
50315 118
C:/> 
C:/> RANDDATA FILL05.DAT 60000 5005
56267 118
C:/> 
C:/> RANDDATA FILL06.DAT 60000 6006
52101 118
C:/> 
C:/> RANDDATA FILL07.DAT 60000 7007
46998 118
C:/> 
C:/> RANDDATA FILL08.DAT 60000 8008
50395 118
C:/> 
C:/> RANDDATA FILL09.DAT 60000 9009
36272 118
C:/> 
C:/> RANDDATA FILL10.DAT 60000 10010
56177 118
C:/> 
C:/> RANDDATA FILL11.DAT 60000 11011
53383 118
C:/> 
C:/> RANDDATA FILL12.DAT 60000 12012
52185 118
C:/> 
C:/> RANDDATA FILL13.DAT 60000 13013
38156 118
C:/> 
C:/> RANDDATA FILL14.DAT 60000 14014
47078 118
C:/> 
C:/> RANDDATA FILL15.DAT 60000 15015
53848 118
C:/> 
C:/> FREE
Free Blocks:  34304 bytes (67 blocks)
Free Memory:  47087 bytes
C:/> 
C:/> # Use up most of the rest (~90 blocks -> ~80 used, ~10 left)
C:/> 
C:/> RANDDATA FILL16.DAT 40000 16016
Error: 6
C:/> 
C:/> FREE
Free Blocks:  0 bytes (0 blocks)
Free Memory:  47087 bytes
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 3: Attempt to create a file that exceeds remaining space
C:/> 
C:/> # RANDDATA creates the file then fails mid-write (partial file)
C:/> 
C:/> RANDDATA TOOBIG.DAT 60000 99999
Error: 6
C:/> 
C:/> # CF also fails when disk is full
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT NOSPACE.TXT
Error: No space.
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 4: Verify existing files are still readable after errors
C:/> 
C:/> SUM FILL01.DAT
50127 118
C:/> 
C:/> SUM FILL08.DAT
50395 118
C:/> 
C:/> SUM FILL13.DAT
38156 118
C:/> 
C:/> SUM FILL16.DAT
6016 66
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 5: Delete some files and verify space is recovered
C:/> 
C:/> RF FILL01.DAT
C:/> 
C:/> RF FILL02.DAT
C:/> 
C:/> FREE
Free Blocks:  121856 bytes (238 blocks)
Free Memory:  47087 bytes
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 6: Create a new file in recovered space (proves reuse)
C:/> 
C:/> RANDDATA REUSE.DAT 10000 55555
5028 20
C:/> 
C:/> SUM REUSE.DAT
5028 20
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 7: Clean up all remaining files
C:/> 
C:/> RF REUSE.DAT
C:/> 
C:/> RF TOOBIG.DAT
Error: Not found.
C:/> 
C:/> # RF NOSPACE.TXT expected to say "Not found" — CF failed on full disk so
C:/> 
C:/> # the file was never created. We attempt removal as a safety net in case
C:/> 
C:/> # CF behavior changes.
C:/> 
C:/> RF NOSPACE.TXT
Error: Not found.
C:/> 
C:/> RF FILL03.DAT
C:/> 
C:/> RF FILL04.DAT
C:/> 
C:/> RF FILL05.DAT
C:/> 
C:/> RF FILL06.DAT
C:/> 
C:/> RF FILL07.DAT
C:/> 
C:/> RF FILL08.DAT
C:/> 
C:/> RF FILL09.DAT
C:/> 
C:/> RF FILL10.DAT
C:/> 
C:/> RF FILL11.DAT
C:/> 
C:/> RF FILL12.DAT
C:/> 
C:/> RF FILL13.DAT
C:/> 
C:/> RF FILL14.DAT
C:/> 
C:/> RF FILL15.DAT
C:/> 
C:/> RF FILL16.DAT
C:/> 
C:/> # Verify filesystem is clean
C:/> 
C:/> DIR
Directory Listing:
    15 SCOTT.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEY.TXT
    55 HELLOWORLD.APP
  1339 RANDDATA.APP
  2050 MULTIFILE.APP
  1238 SIZETEST.APP
  1108 MORE.APP
  1579 WC.APP
  1830 TAIL.APP
  1158 HEAD.APP
  1318 APPEND.APP
     4 ONE.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEYF.TXT
     6 THREE.TXT
 <DIR> MYDIR
     4 SIX.TXT
     6 SEVEN.TXT
     6 EIGHT.TXT
     7 TWELVE.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> FREE
Free Blocks:  948224 bytes (1852 blocks)
Free Memory:  47087 bytes
C:/> 
C:/> HALT
CPU halted
